Features

	Termcaps prompt		Left / Right arrows allow you to edit your cmd
		 		Up / Down arrows show previous cmd
				CTRL-D exits
				CTRL-L clears the screen
				CTRL-C aff a new prompt
				Tab autocompletion

	History			history cmd aff history
				history -c remove history
				!! !n !-n and !str available

	Quotes			cmd "str of args"

	Globing			Use regex in your cmd

	Background		cmd & run cmd in background

	variable		set, unset, $var

	Alias			set alias

